## **Benefits of the Bulkhead Pattern**

âœ”ï¸ **Fault Isolation** â€“ Failures are contained.  
âœ”ï¸ **Resilience** â€“ One bad service doesnâ€™t bring down the entire system.  
âœ”ï¸ **Better Resource Management** â€“ Each service gets dedicated resources.  
âœ”ï¸ **Improved User Experience** â€“ Users can still use parts of the app even if one module fails.

