## **Conclusion: Why Bulkhead Pattern Matters**

The **Bulkhead Pattern** is a proven strategy to build **fault-tolerant systems**. By isolating failures, it ensures that one broken part doesnâ€™t sink the whole ship.

So next time youâ€™re designing a system, ask yourself:  
ğŸ‘‰ *If this part fails, will my whole app go down?*

